OL,3,CSam Neill, star of Jurassic Park and
OL,4,CPeaky Blinders, has died aged 78
OL,6,FSam Neill, the New Zealand actor best
OL,7,Fknown for his leading role in the
OL,8,Fblockbuster Jurassic Park franchise
OL,9,Fand in BBC series Peaky Blinders, has
OL,10,Fdied at the age of 78.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for Neill's family
OL,13,Fconfirmed he died on Monday,
OL,14,Fsurrounded by his family.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
