OL,3,CSam Neill, star of Jurassic Park and
OL,4,CPeaky Blinders, has died aged 78
OL,6,FPaying tribute, Australian Prime
OL,7,FMinister Anthony Albanese said: "Sam
OL,8,FNeill starred in so many beloved
OL,9,FAustralian stories and he earned a
OL,10,Fspecial place in Australian hearts.
OL,12,F"Wry and dry, thoughtful and laconic,
OL,13,FSam fought illness with the same
OL,14,Fdignity, hu
OL,16,Fmour and conviction that gave strength
OL,17,Fto his every performance.
OL,19,F"He will be much mourned and long
OL,20,Fremembered. May he rest in peace."
OL,26,@oD@aOUtD@AOU{D@AOU|D@bO]
