OL,3,CSam Neill, star of Jurassic Park and
OL,4,CPeaky Blinders, has died aged 78
OL,6,FNeill was born Nigel John Dermot Neill
OL,7,Fin the Northern Ireland town of Omagh
OL,8,Fin 1947. His family moved to New
OL,9,FZealand when he was seven.
OL,11,FDuring his time at school, the
OL,12,Fprevalence of other students named
OL,13,FNigel inspired Neill to assume the
OL,14,Ffirst name "Sam".
OL,16,FHe went on to study English literature
OL,17,Fat the University of Canterbury.
OL,26,@vD@LOUvD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
