OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1784053120
OL,3,CSam Neill, star of Jurassic Park and
OL,4,CPeaky Blinders, has died aged 78
OL,6,FHis breakthrough came in 1993's
OL,7,FJurassic Park, a franchise he later
OL,8,Freturned to in Jurassic Park III and
OL,9,F2022's Jurassic World Dominion.
OL,11,FNeill earned acclaim for performances
OL,12,Fin films including The Piano, The Hunt
OL,13,FFor Red October, and Hunt For The
OL,14,FWilderpeople.
OL,16,FHe also found success on television,
OL,17,Fplaying Major Chester Campbell in the
OL,18,Ffirst two seasons of Peaky Blinders,
OL,19,Fwith further appearances in The
OL,20,FTudors, The Simpsons and Alcatraz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
